"Some say in ice"

16
00:02:35,805 --> 00:02:40,504
"From what I've tasted of desire
I hold with those who favor fire"

17
00:02:42,678 --> 00:02:45,203
"But if I had to perish twice"

18
00:02:47,183 --> 00:02:49,777
"I think I know enough of hate"

19
00:02:49,852 --> 00:02:52,878
"To say that for destruction ice"

20
00:02:54,657 --> 00:02:56,489
"Is also great"

21
00:02:58,328 --> 00:03:00,125
"And would suffice"

22
